<subSubSection pageId="18" pageNumber="107" type="description">
<paragraph pageId="18" pageNumber="107">Culture characteristics.</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="18" pageNumber="107">Colony growth on PDA originally white, becoming pale yellowish after 7-10 days. Colony flat, felty-like, with a uniform texture and yellowish to dark brown conidiomata irregularly scattered on the colony surface.</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection pageId="18" pageNumber="107" type="materials_examined">
<paragraph pageId="18" pageNumber="107">Additional specimens examined (paratypes).</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="18" pageNumber="107">
CHINA. Shaanxi Province: Ankang City, Ningshan County, Huoditang Forest Farm, 
<geoCoordinate direction="north" orientation="latitude" precision="1" value="36.437027">36°26'13.30&quot;N</geoCoordinate>
, 
